txt.en: 'Oh, look at all these frogs, sitting, and hopping, and croaking! I still miss Croaker, but I'm very happy with all my new friends! I guess I'll have to name them all. Where to start?!'
There are many occupants of the hidden village of Lyndelby who are curious to meet with you.

'Oh, look at all these frogs, sitting, and hopping, and croaking! Thank you, [placeholder]... I still miss Croaker, but I'm very happy with all my new friends. That one there looks just like Croaker, so I think I'll name him Croaker the Second!\n\n'Why, I guess I'll have to name them all! Where to start?!'
Odger Túcca can be found in Lyndelby.\n\nYou should bring Odger Túcca the frogs that you collected.

'Oh, [placeholder]...

'My pet frog, Croaker, just today passed away. You remember him, don't you? Always croaking—and jumping! Well, you know how frogs are!

'You know me, I like frogs. Always had a frog as a pet... ever since I was little. And now I don't have any! I ought to just go down to the river and look for another, but I'm too sad right now. Twenty seasons Croaker and I spent together... it is just terrible!

'You've been helping everyone else today, haven't you? You sure would bring a smile to old Odger here if you found me a new pet frog to call my own!'
'Oh, look at all these frogs, sitting, and hopping, and croaking!'
Frogs can be found in Lyndelby.\n\nYou should collect frogs for Odger Túcca.

'I like frogs. Always had a frog as a pet... ever since I was little. Now I don't have any. My pet frog, Croaker, just today passed away. I should go down to the river to get another, but I'm too sad right now. You know, you sure would bring a smile to Odger here if you got me a new frog pet.'
Bring Odger Túcca the frogs you collected
Talk to Odger Túcca in Lyndelby
